<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입</title>

    <!-- jquery -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.5.1/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-u1OknCvxWvY5kfmNBILK2hRnQC3Pr17a+RTT6rIHI7NnikvbZlHgTPOOmMi466C8" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- main js -->
    <script defer src="../js/login.js"></script>

    <!-- css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">

</head>
<body id="login">
    <div class="container-lg d-flex flex-column align-items-center bg-light p-5 rounded-0" id="register">
        <h2>로그인</h2>
        <form action="/login" method="POST" class="w-100" name="login">
            <p id="err" class="mt-3" style="display: none;">아이디(로그인 전용 아이디), 비밀번호를 잘못 입력했습니다. 입력하신 내용을 다시 확인해주세요.</p>
            <div class="mt-3 id">
                <label class="mb-2" for="input-email">아이디</label>
                <input type="text" name="id" class="form-control rounded-0" id="id" />
                <input hidden="hidden" />
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-3 password">
                <label class="mb-2" for="input-pw">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="text" name="pw" class="form-control rounded-0" id="pw" />
            </div>
            
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4 password">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary rounded-0 w-100" onclick="loginClick()">로그인</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>